@NODE "Requirements" "Requirements."
@TOC "MAINS"

   @{B}@{FG SHINE}=====»@{FG TEXT} Requirements. @{FG SHINE}«=====@{FG TEXT}@{UB}

   You need an AMIGA with CHIP mem, more CHIP mem is better. Bacause the
   modules is stored in CHIP. I will fix so they will be stored in FAST mem
   insted bacause most of all AMIGA owners has more FAST then CHIP. :)

   The program has been tested on the following computers:

   A1200   420MB HD+2,1GB HD   2MB CHIP 4 MB FAST   WB3.1   OS 3.0
   A2000   170MB HD            1MB CHIP 8 MB FAST   WB3.1   OS 3.1

   There is a little problem on my friends A2000 bacause he only have 1MB
   CHIP and when the WB has been loaded it`s only 907K CHIP left. So you
   can`t load modules that is bigger than 907K and when the program supports
   17 modules there will be a problem i you try to fill all 17 places.

@ENDNODE

@NODE "Registration" "Registration."
@TOC "MAINE"
 
   @{B}@{FG SHINE}=====»@{FG TEXT} Registration. @{FG SHINE}«=====@{FG TEXT}@{UB}

   The registration fee is 30SEK, 4US$. I don`t think that it`s too much for
   this program. You must add 1US$ if you live outside Scandinavia, because
   it ain`t cheap to send something to another country.

   The things that I have disabled in the UNREGISTERED version is the
   Save Prefs function; you can`t save the colours or which modules that
   should load when you start the program. That`s the only disadvantage with
   the UNREGISTERED copy.

   To register you must send an envelope whith 30SEK or 4US$. DON`T send any
   coins if you use US$, because I can`t change coins to Swedish money and
   then you won`t recieve the program. Put a paper around the money just for
   safety, you never know what the people in the post office does. :)
   I know that sending money to a stranger ain`t the funniest thing to do,
   but I guarantee that everyone in Sweden will recieve the program within
   one week, IF the post office don`t screew up, I don`t know how long it
   takes to send it to another country. Don`t forget to send the
   @{"registration form" LINK "Registration form"} along with the money, without it I can`t send the
   program to you.

   If you register you will of course recive the latest version of
   the program, you will also recive my Yazzii which is PD.

   @{"Click here for my adress." LINK "Author"

@ENDNODE

@NODE "Registration form" "Registration form."
@TOC "MAINE"

   @{B}@{FG SHINE}=====»@{FG TEXT} Registration paper. @{FG SHINE}«=====@{FG TEXT}@{UB}

   This is how the form should look like.
   Start the program and go to the registration screen, take Print there if
   you have a printer, otherwise just draw it on a regular paper and fill it
